attributes.action: Deport people with dual nationality who are found guilty of raping children
attributes.background: We think the Grooming Gangs scandal is possibly the biggest scandal in our country's history. It is time for a tough approach. We are calling for foreign born nationals with dual nationality who are found guilty of raping children to be deported.
